    AnonymousEvent

    Wrapper for the database operations
    Event Deprecated

    EventDispatcher
    Thread that runs in background and dispatches the events to the server.

    EventTracker
    Global tracker for events.
    EventUtils

    LegacyEventDispatcher

    LegacyEventSerializer
    Serializer for legacy events
